title: FC Annecy - Wikipedia
snippet: Annecy Football Club was founded under its current name in 1993 as the reincarnation of the defunct Football Club d'Annecy. FC Annecy, formed in 1927, spent the majority of their history in regional amateur football. The club turned professional in 1942, but was compelled to return to amateurism ...

title: Football Club d'Annecy — Wikipédia
snippet: Le Football Club d'Annecy est fondé en 1927 par René Veyrat, René Favre-Hoffer-Moschberger, Johanny Bolluz, Goerges Rulland, Georges Sonjon et Eugène Perron. Le premier président du club est alors Louis Monnet. En 1933, Jean Chatenoud est nommé président.
